headline: Illinois American Water Completes Acquisition of City of Madison Wastewater Collections System
summary: MADISON, Ill., September 30, 2025--The City of Madison Wastewater Collections Systems Adds Approximately 1,500 Wastewater Customers to Company’s Metro East Footprint Near St. Louis.
